{"type": "article", "id": 15524, "title": "“彼此”磁力贴", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-25T06:30:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153837er4L967PRqanwKWN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是的一个矿石形态磁力贴，任意两块都合在一起成为完整的正八面体，但分开的时候只是看起来相似的完全不同的多面体。设计师想要以此表达相爱的两个人走到一起，合成完整的“结晶”，但分开时也是两个很有个性的人。磁力贴是石膏做的，有 6 种颜色搭配。<a href=\"http://www.yiyanzao.com/index.php?p=pro_show&amp;id=23&amp;l=2\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142605TPkI4z5UYBoSqXWN.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142606Z36VINUlraFnGWmd.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"429\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.446875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142606ROaso9N7XIi5bmhK.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261426062wcuZxgTPKv53tm1.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142607F7f46v9POeImTzKH.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}